data.description: Southside charmer for sale! This spacious 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home has cathedral ceilings in the living room & primary bedroom. There is also a second dining area & a wet bar. The roof was replaced in 2017. This house is located on the Southside of Corpus Christi and is ready for its newest owner! Call your favorite REALTOR® and schedule your showing today!
